{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019620/extras/ShootoutGIF.gif?t=1728994281\" /><br><br>Inspired by games such as:  <strong>Ready or Not</strong>, <strong>Rainbow Six: Siege</strong>, <strong>CoD: Modern Warfare</strong> and <strong>Insurgency: Sandstorm</strong>. GERONIMO is a highly realistic, tactical and immersive CQB shooter that has been built from the ground up for Virtual Reality. Play Solo, or with your friends and carry out your operations through our missions, some even inspired by real world raids.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019620/extras/BREACHING.png?t=1728994281\" /><br>Breaching is a key feature in GERONIMO. A wide range of methods are available, one or more of which may be used in any given situation. Use an arsenal of tools to open doors and get your team into the target building.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>IMPROVISE, ADAPT, OVERCOME.</i></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019620/extras/BreachingWithEnemyGIF.gif?t=1728994281\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019620/extras/DYNAMICAI.png?t=1728994281\" /><br>Inspired by CoD: Modern Warfare missions such as &quot;Clean House&quot; and &quot;Wolf's Den&quot;, GERONIMO brings an unpredictable dynamic A.I. to the game that enforces you to think, act and decide quickly because lives depend on it. The A.I. will hide in closets, beds and use every possible advantage they can get in a room. Barricaded shooters, MG nests settled down the hallway, Suicide bombers, everything is possible...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN BEING A COWARD AND A HERO IS NOT WHETHER YOU'RE SCARED, IT'S WHAT YOU DO WHILE YOU'RE SCARED.</i></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam